item.title: Jake Bugg: The Bugg Brand
item.author: Simran Sansoy,
item.description: I was lucky enough to get the chance to see Jake Bugg last Thursday at one of his three sold out gigs at the O2 Academy in Brixton. I’m only familiar with a handful of his songs, so I was actually quite surprised by his performance as a musician, singer and songwriter. Some people say he lacks …
